	<term>MyFrame <emphasis remap='I'>"frame_name"</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies a frame definition (window decor in general)  and is covered in the MyFrame section of the documentation.
		Please also note that window decor can be defined on a per window basis if needed in the database.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="MyFrame#synopsis">MyFrame definition</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
